17/02 4:34:05 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umarlmonk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MarlMonk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/17/02 8:50:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=572.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Anyone use masks in PVP?</span><hr size=1> Sounds hilarious :)<br><br>And it might work, unless you look at the name of the person who challenged you.  'Soandso has challenged you to a duel to the death!'  and when you target that dark elf far in the distance, the name that appears in your targetting box will be 'Soandso3' or whatnot.<br><br>So, it might work, as I said earlier, but only if the duelist/'duelee' isn't paying very good attention. <p>I am the diversion of me.</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umarlmonk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MarlMonk</A> at: 1/17/02 8:51:33 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uikssar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ikss Ar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/18/02 12:23:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=572.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Anyone use masks in PVP?</span><hr size=1> i've used my iksar mask on several occasions to get the drop on an evil / group of evils, they just sit there and look at you and you get a few free stabs before they know whats what =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utheaos.showPublicPr